Input details

0poid    POIDIn Out
Userequired
Modedbonly
Class/service/pcm_client

Dummy poid used for database only.

0int    FLAGSIn Out
Useoptional

Flag value indicates the type of object to be retrieved. Flag value 0x10 for product, 0x20 for discount and 0x40 for sponsorship. Product, discount and/or sponsorship can be retrieved by combining these three values. Flag value 0x0008 to retrieve tailor-made products as well from Oracle Monetization Cloud.

0string    PERMITTEDIn Out
Useoptional
Max length255

Service type. This field is used when either product or discount objects are required.

0timestamp    MOD_TIn Out
Useoptional

Modified time. This field is used when either product or discount or sponsorship objects are required. Total time in seconds w.r.t. server Time Zone.

0string    NAMEIn Out
Useoptional
Max length255

Object name. Object can be product, discount or sponsorship.

0substruct    CONTEXT_INFOIn Out
Useoptional

Substruct to pass information from external clients.

1string    CORRELATION_IDIn Out
Useoptional
Parent in.CONTEXT_INFO
Max length128

Correlation id passed by an external system to Oracle Monetization Cloud.

1string    EXTERNAL_USERIn Out
Useoptional
Parent in.CONTEXT_INFO
Max length128

User of an external system connecting to Oracle Monetization Cloud.
